###

### Get bank detail by Employee ID
GET {{Moongazing.Allio.Employee.Api_HostAddress}}/api/allio/bankdetails/by-employee-id/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Get bank detail by IBAN
GET {{Moongazing.Allio.Employee.Api_HostAddress}}/api/allio/bankdetails/by-iban/TR000000000000000000000000
