###

### Get bank details by Bank Name (paginated)
GET {{Moongazing.Allio.Employee.Api_HostAddress}}/api/allio/bankdetails/by-bank-name/Ziraat?page=0&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get bank details by Currency (paginated)
GET {{Moongazing.Allio.Employee.Api_HostAddress}}/api/allio/bankdetails/by-currecny/TRY?page=0&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get bank details by Dynamic Filter (paginated)
POST {{Moongazing.Allio.Employee.Api_HostAddress}}/api/allio/bankdetails/filter?page=0&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "field": "bankName",
      "operator": "Contains",
      "value": "Ziraat"
    },
    {
      "field": "currency",
      "operator": "Equals",
      "value": "TRY"
    }
  ],
  "sorts": [
    {
      "field": "bankName",
      "direction": "ASC"
    }
  ]
}
